  <script type="text/javascript">
   function ValidateOrder() {
            // Show Registration If Any Information Is Not Present.
            var IsDisabled = 0;

            if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtFName').value == "") {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtFName').style.background = 'Yellow';
                IsDisabled++;
            }
            else {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtFName').style.background = 'White';
            }

            if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtLName').value == "") {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtLName').style.background = 'Yellow';
                IsDisabled++;
            }
            else {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtLName').style.background = 'White';
            }

            if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtEmail').value == "") {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtEmail').style.background = 'Yellow';
                IsDisabled++;
            }
            else {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtEmail').style.background = 'White';
            }

            if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtAddress').value == "") {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtAddress').style.background = 'Yellow';
                IsDisabled++;
            }
            else {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtAddress').style.background = 'White';
            }

            if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtCity').value == "") {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtCity').style.background = 'Yellow';
                IsDisabled++;
            }
            else {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtCity').style.background = 'White';
            }

            if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtZip').value == "") {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtZip').style.background = 'Yellow';
                IsDisabled++;
            }
            else {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtZip').style.background = 'White';
            }

            if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtState').value == "") {
                if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_drpCountryCode').value == "" || document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_drpCountryCode').value == "CAN") {
                    document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtState').style.background = 'Yellow';
                    IsDisabled++;
                }
                else {
                    document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtState').style.background = 'White';
                }
            }
            else {
                if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_drpCountryCode').value != "") {
                    if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_drpCountryCode').value != "CAN") {
                        document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtState').value = "";
                    }
                }
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtState').style.background = 'White';
            }

            if (document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtPhone').value == "") {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtPhone').style.background = 'Yellow';
                IsDisabled++;
            }
            else {
                document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_CPH_CPH_AddressBilling_txtPhone').style.background = 'White';
            }
            if (IsDisabled == 0) {
                return true;
            }
            else {
                return false;
            }
        }
  </script>

          <br/>
          <br/>
          Tough, durable and lightweight, bamboo is a natural in the kitchen. One of nature's most sustainable resources, bamboo is stronger than oak and reaches maturity in just four years  without pesticides. Bamboo's density makes it naturally water-resistant, which inhibits germs and bacteria. It won't scratch your pans like metal and doesn't absorb moisture like conventional wood.
          <br/>
          <br/>
          Though used like timber, bamboo is a grass that self-propagates as it spreads underground via a network of rhizomes.
